sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Shop as Shopify
    participant Pub as PublicApi
    participant DB as orchestrator schema
    participant Bus as Wolverine bus
    participant Wrk as Worker
    participant Route as RoutingEngine
    participant Pnl as PostNL InMemory
    participant Proj as ProjectionHandlers
    participant Read as ops_read + customer_read

    rect rgb(255,230,230)
    Shop--xPub: order.created webhook<br/>NOT IMPLEMENTED
    end

    Pub->>Pub: POST /v1/shipments/batches<br/>(manual or future webhook)
    Pub->>DB: CreateShipmentBatch + Shipments<br/>(idempotency check)
    Pub->>Bus: ShipmentBatchAccepted, ShipmentCreated*N
    Pub-->>Pub: 202 + cascading ProcessShipmentBatchCommand
    Bus->>Proj: events
    Proj->>Read: insert batch+shipments rows

    Bus->>Wrk: ProcessShipmentBatchCommand
    Wrk->>DB: batch.StartProcessing
    Wrk->>Bus: RequestCarrierLabel * N

    loop per shipment
        Bus->>Wrk: RequestCarrierLabelCommand
        Wrk->>Route: SelectCarrier(shipment, assignments)
        Route-->>Wrk: CarrierCode + scoring trail
        Wrk->>Pnl: CreateLabelAsync
        Pnl-->>Wrk: tracking + labelUri (or failure)
        Wrk->>DB: Shipment.RecordLabel / Fail<br/>Batch.RecordItem*
        Wrk->>Bus: ShipmentCarrierSelected, ShipmentLabeled/Failed
        Wrk->>DB: fresh scope -> RecheckCompletion
    end

    Wrk->>Bus: ShipmentBatchCompleted (last writer wins)
    Bus->>Proj: events
    Proj->>Read: status, KPI bumps

    rect rgb(255,230,230)
    Wrk--xShop: PushFulfillmentAsync<br/>STUB - only logs
    end
